ygData.subject: RE: Missing bard songs
ygData.msgSnippet: I am assuming they are not implemented yet, as in a patch last month they added level 43 and 50 songs, and previously they added the fufil s and tuyen s songs.
ygData.messageBody:
I am assuming they are not implemented yet, as in a patch last month they
added level 43 and 50 songs, and previously they added the fufil's and
tuyen's songs. Plus songs that high level would probably be quests that
would not give a "too experienced" message. My guess is they will be on
vendors in later patches (when dammit?!?! hehehe)

Shada
